snippet.title: Green Phoenix [Switch/PC] Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
Green Phoenix is an on-rails 3D space shooter mixed with a deep narrative experience that focuses on the concept of ego and the meaning of freedom.


More details here: https://worthplaying.com/game/15232/



Green Phoenix is coming to PC (Steam) and Nintendo Switch on May 27, 2021 for 2.99€.
